               whence <bibl><title>SEG</title> <citedRange>9.60</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="gray1956"/> <citedRange>p.59</citedRange></bibl>, on which see
               <bibl><ptr target="jmr-rgg1957"/><citedRange>273</citedRange></bibl>, whence  
               <bibl><ptr target="robertBE"/> <citedRange>1959.511</citedRange></bibl>, 
               <bibl><title>SEG</title> <citedRange>17.811</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
         </div>

         

         <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
